{"tid":413219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8 改用支那製玻璃棄美製一跌即爆   蘋果用次級元件捱批","createTime":"2017-09-25T10:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T11:20:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f05f679bca8b661dfbe1c6aea2fb578e4a5a38","tid":413219,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/09/25/netizen-complaint-why-iphone-8-glass-so-weak/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2Fnetizen-complaint-why-iphone-8-glass-so-weak%2F&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=77010ebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/09/25/netizen-complaint-why-iphone-8-glass-so-weak/</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone 8 機背玻璃一跌就爆？！網民指脆弱有因！<br />\n<br />\n因為無線充電 iPhone 8 決定使用玻璃外殼，令 iPhone 8 的機身有點像玉石的質地，非常美觀，但是在耐久度方面，早前在不少測試之中似乎有點脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n於是有網民就概嘆 iPhone 8 的玻璃大不如前，一名網民在 Facebook 群組「iOS 技術交流區」爆料指，iPhone 8 機背玻璃並不是美國康寧的大猩猩玻璃，而是中國的藍思科技的玻璃，但他認為由藍思科技提供的 iPhone 8 玻璃沒有 iPhone 4s 般堅硬，一跌即爆，技術貿素不佳，更批評蘋果成了降低成本賺到盡而用上「次級」元件。<br />\n<br />\n在 2010 和 2011 年發佈的 iPhone 4/4s，機背一樣使用玻璃製作，但 iPhone 4/4s 的玻璃是由蘋果自家開發，聲稱已一般膠片硬 30 倍，並交由一直提供 iPhone 螢幕玻璃的康寧代工生產，在當時不少網民稱許 iPhone 4 的玻璃硬度好，不易跌破。"},{"pid":"f698544f7b56500545df076e990c0a3073805108","tid":413219,"uid":7840,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a720dc8a407d6708a27aae032ea4020db09e054","tid":413219,"uid":9286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:24:30.000Z","msg":"我用左咁多年smartphone 都未試過跌爆/跌花"},{"pid":"85f26c0a4d74bda8ae33d64f121c1423a0abc88b","tid":413219,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"會跌手機嘅都係手殘"},{"pid":"33c9c16224c188c8de4881edd17b416e32346e33","tid":413219,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>